Notes:

To intall the standalone IDE, download and install:
 - OSX: fantomide-x.y.z.app.tgz
 - Linux/Windows: fantomide-x.y.z.zip

To install the plugin:

IMPORTANT:update.xml mow points to a plugin built for netbeans 6.9
For netbeans 6.8 point to nb6.8-updates.xml instead.

  - Open Netbeans
  - Go to tools / plugins
  - Go to settings tab (List of update centers), click "Add"
  - Add -> Name: Fantom Url: http://cdn.bitbucket.org/tcolar/fantomide/downloads/updates.xml
  - Press OK to save it
  - Go to "Available plugins" Tab (sort by Name)
  - Select the checkbox next to "Fantom"
  - Click "Install"
  - Follow the wizzrad (Next/Install), ignore the "Not trusted" warning (Continue)
  - Click Finish and close the plugins panel.
  - Restart Netbeans
